-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sleuth
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
- makes it possible to identify logs to a specific job, thread, or request

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sleuth Token
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
contains:
- application name
- trace id (given by sleuth, same in all services for one request)
- span id (given by sleuth, same in the same unit of work => method)
- exportToZipkin flag

INFO [book-service,cdb908ecdb6c16ef,cdb908ecdb6c16ef,false]

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
spring.sleuth.sampler.percentage
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
How many of the requests will be traced in percent
- 1 => 100% (all requests are traced)
- default = 0.1 (10%)

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sampler
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Sampler Bean can be created manually
- override isSampled() to decide, if a given Span should be traced